{"arkId":"cl010099483","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099483","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ovale","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ovale"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Henri IV (1589-1610) (Occident-\u003ERenaissance-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1600 - 1615","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1600,"endYear":1615,"imprecision":"","text":"D\u00e9but du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Flant,Jean","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1616","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 7043","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre ovale ; les deux couvercles d\u00e9cor\u00e9s de bas-reliefs inspir\u00e9s de plaquettes de Valerio Belli ; celui du cadran repr\u00e9sente un sacrifice : six personnages drap\u00e9s \u00e0 l\u0027antique encadrent un autel cylindrique, situ\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u0027avant d\u0027un portique \u00e0 quatre colonnes ioniques portant un fronton cintr\u00e9. Celui du mouvement figure un mariage : les mari\u00e9s sont b\u00e9nis par l\u0027Amour juch\u00e9 sur un autel. Au revers, un cadran solaire et une boussole. Carrure orn\u00e9e d\u0027une frise grav\u00e9e de rinceaux fleuris o\u00f9 sont \u00e9tendues deux femmes nues. Pendant en forme de chapiteau. Cadran grav\u00e9 de rinceaux peupl\u00e9s d\u0027oiseaux, t\u00eates fantastiques et d\u0027un mufle de lion. Anneau horaire \u00e0 chiffres romains. Mouvement, ajust\u00e9 dans le bo\u00eetier, muni d\u0027un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre et d\u0027une fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau. Coq et cliquet grav\u00e9s d\u0027un d\u00e9cor floral.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Flant\/AR","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"6,8","displayDimension":"6,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"4","displayDimension":"4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,6","displayDimension":"2,6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"La Rochelle (Poitou-Charentes = Poitou Charentes-\u003ECharente-Maritime = Charente Maritime)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Charles Stein (1840-1899), vente \u00e0 Paris galerie Georges Petit 10-14 mai 1886 n\u00b0 220 ; collection Paul Garnier (1834-1916), \u00e0 Paris. Don Paul Garnier, en 1916.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Garnier, Paul ","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"M. Stein, Charles","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1916","startYear":1916,"endYear":1916}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"period":[{"value":"Henri IV (1589-1610)"}],"place":[{"value":"La Rochelle"}],"objectType":[{"value":"horlogerie"},{"value":"montr